Package: coda.count
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Compositional Count Data Distributions
Version: 0.3.7
Date: 2022-03-07
Authors@R: c(person("Marc", "Comas-Cuf√≠", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
                    email = "mcomas@imae.udg.edu"))
Description: Different tools for counting distributions defined on the simplex. Most distributions are based on
    the log-ratio approach introduced by John Aitchison (1982) <http://www.jstor.org/stable/2345821>. Main functions
    have been implemented in c++ for better performance.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.2)
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 0.12.12),
    coda.base (>= 0.2.1)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo, RcppEnsmallen
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
NeedsCompilation: yes
RoxygenNote: 7.2.0
